---
interface Props {
  lang: string;
  t: (key: string) => string;
  briefs: Array<{ title: string; slug: string; category?: string; commentary?: string }>;
  tools: Array<{ title: string; slug: string; category?: string; pricing?: string; bestFor?: string }>;
  cases: Array<{ title: string; slug: string; industry?: string; revenue?: string; problemType?: string }>;
}
const { lang, briefs, tools, cases } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">{lang === 'zh' ? '// READING PATHS' : lang === 'ja' ? '// READING PATHS' : '// READING PATHS'}</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">
      {lang === 'zh' ? '从哪里开始读，一眼就清楚' : lang === 'ja' ? 'どこから読み始めるかがすぐ分かる' : 'Three ways into the site'}
    </h2>
    <p class="section-desc">
      {lang === 'zh' ? '首页最重要的不是解释功能，而是把不同内容组织成清晰的阅读路径。' : lang === 'ja' ? 'トップで大切なのは機能説明ではなく、読む導線をはっきり見せることです。' : 'The homepage should help readers choose a starting point fast: what is new, what is worth evaluating, and what is working in practice.'}
    </p>

    <div class="desk-grid">
      <article class="desk-card animate-in">
        <div class="desk-topline">
          <span class="desk-tag">01</span>
          <a href={`/${lang}/daily/`} class="desk-link">{lang === 'zh' ? '进入每日简报' : lang === 'ja' ? 'デイリーブリーフへ' : 'Open daily brief'}</a>
        </div>
        <div class="desk-intro">
          <h3>{lang === 'zh' ? 'Daily Brief' : lang === 'ja' ? 'Daily Brief' : 'Daily Brief'}</h3>
          <p>{lang === 'zh' ? '每天 3 到 5 条值得看、且对 AI 一人公司真有影响的更新。' : lang === 'ja' ? '毎日3〜5本、AIソロ事業に本当に影響のある更新だけ。' : 'Three to five updates a day, filtered for actual relevance to AI solopreneurs.'}</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="desk-list">
          {briefs.length > 0 ? briefs.map((brief) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/${lang}/daily/${brief.slug}/`}>{brief.title}</a>
              <span>{brief.commentary || brief.category || (lang === 'zh' ? '信号' : lang === 'ja' ? 'シグナル' : 'Signal')}</span>
            </li>
          )) : (
            <li class="empty-row">{lang === 'zh' ? 'Notion 内容接入后会显示最新条目。' : lang === 'ja' ? 'Notion接続後に最新記事を表示します。' : 'Latest entries will appear here once Notion is connected.'}</li>
          )}
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="desk-card animate-in delay-1">
        <div class="desk-topline">
          <span class="desk-tag">02</span>
          <a href={`/${lang}/tools/`} class="desk-link">{lang === 'zh' ? '浏览工具评测' : lang === 'ja' ? 'ツールレビューへ' : 'Browse reviews'}</a>
        </div>
        <div class="desk-intro">
          <h3>{lang === 'zh' ? 'Tool Deep Dives' : lang === 'ja' ? 'Tool Deep Dives' : 'Tool Deep Dives'}</h3>
          <p>{lang === 'zh' ? '用结构化评测替代纯工具目录，重点回答值不值得用、适合谁、怎样接入工作流。' : lang === 'ja' ? '単なるツール一覧ではなく、価値、対象読者、ワークフロー適合性を評価します。' : 'Structured reviews that answer whether a tool is worth the money, who it serves, and how it fits a real workflow.'}</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="desk-list">
          {tools.length > 0 ? tools.map((tool) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/${lang}/tools/${tool.slug}/`}>{tool.title}</a>
              <span>{tool.bestFor || tool.pricing || tool.category || 'AI'}</span>
            </li>
          )) : (
            <li class="empty-row">{lang === 'zh' ? '优先把高质量旧文迁成首批评测。' : lang === 'ja' ? '旧記事の良質コンテンツから最初のレビューを整備。' : 'Migrate the best legacy pages into your first review set.'}</li>
          )}
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="desk-card animate-in delay-2">
        <div class="desk-topline">
          <span class="desk-tag">03</span>
          <a href={`/${lang}/cases/`} class="desk-link">{lang === 'zh' ? '查看案例' : lang === 'ja' ? 'ケースを見る' : 'View case studies'}</a>
        </div>
        <div class="desk-intro">
          <h3>{lang === 'zh' ? 'Case Studies' : lang === 'ja' ? 'Case Studies' : 'Case Studies'}</h3>
          <p>{lang === 'zh' ? '把过去按行业散落的内容重组为“问题导向”的案例库，更贴近创业者决策。' : lang === 'ja' ? '業界別の断片的な情報を、課題別のケースに再構成します。' : 'Reframe scattered industry pages into problem-led cases about growth, operations, and productization.'}</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="desk-list">
          {cases.length > 0 ? cases.map((item) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/${lang}/cases/${item.slug}/`}>{item.title}</a>
              <span>{item.problemType || item.revenue || item.industry || (lang === 'zh' ? '案例' : lang === 'ja' ? 'ケース' : 'Case')}</span>
            </li>
          )) : (
            <li class="empty-row">{lang === 'zh' ? '下一阶段适合把旧站行业页改写成案例库。' : lang === 'ja' ? '次の段階で業界ページをケースへ再編集。' : 'Next phase: rewrite legacy industry pages into strong case studies.'}</li>
          )}
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-block { padding: 80px 0; }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .section-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 700px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .desk-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .desk-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 420px;
  }
  .desk-intro {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .desk-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: var(--bg-card-hover);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }
  .desk-topline {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .desk-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .desk-link {
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .desk-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 0.98;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .desk-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .desk-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .desk-list li {
    display: grid;
    gap: 6px;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .desk-list a {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .desk-list span,
  .empty-row {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .empty-row {
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-block { padding: 64px 0; }
    .desk-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .desk-card {
      min-height: unset;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
